{"tid":342679,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"顛覆你們長久以來錯誤的觀念， 除了霸氣、“力”的作用同樣重要","createTime":"2017-07-31T19:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T04:56:44.000Z","uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f91fa796ba46c8bff22dfef986b7c4aa71858f9","tid":342679,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T19:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/035744_538c01bb1ba176e427f0b5a1bff4687b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F035744_538c01bb1ba176e427f0b5a1bff4687b.jpg&h=9be79457&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/035744_536a7835198ff392ef746d095c984c7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F035744_536a7835198ff392ef746d095c984c7e.jpg&h=073f185e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/035835_e70d7ea2b4e0027c42194e8cf4600371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F035835_e70d7ea2b4e0027c42194e8cf4600371.jpg&h=5eaba3e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52525231a25ab4ea7c15b82ceb38036da1caab56","tid":342679,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T19:59:27.000Z","msg":"你們長久以來存在一個錯誤的觀念，就是認為武裝色霸氣決定一切而忽視了&ldquo;力&rdquo;的作用，假設一個人練到的武裝色數值只有&ldquo;10&rdquo;，那麼除非他通過修煉或升級的方式來提升這個數值，否則他就不可能發動超過這個數值&ldquo;10&rdquo;的武裝色，因為這是他&rdquo;目前最高&ldquo;的水平，那麼他要在這個目前最高的武裝色的水平下打出更強大的攻擊力就要靠&ldquo;力量&rdquo;了！而&ldquo;力量&rdquo;是可以根據招式和狀態或者其它因素而改變的，這就是為什麼2檔、3擋、4擋、大猿王之間的攻擊力存在差距了，這就是&rdquo;力&ldquo;的重要性如果按你們說的武裝色決定一切那麼&rdquo;234檔&ldquo;就沒有存在的意義了，而&rdquo;四擋&ldquo;的威力強大之處就是在於橡皮的特性&ldquo;彈性&rdquo; ，它能通過彈性縮進去打出更強大的力量！"},{"pid":"19b7243afa6ebf31ffd53f80261dbf126ab45996","tid":342679,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"而克力架砍傷了四擋路飛的手臂並不是因為什麼破防、什麼武裝色之間的高低，而是因為下圖那樣，，四擋路飛的&ldquo;力&quot;是向前衝先和餅乾鎧甲對碰再直接打碎餅乾鎧甲的，而克力架本體是躲開了四擋的&quot;力&rdquo;突然冒出來砍在了不需要和四擋的&ldquo;力&rdquo;對碰的薄弱位置！所以我之前開貼說過 如果像下面圖2那樣對碰 結果就會不一樣了"},{"pid":"761b5d6a519121c546f9bb9e4c1accad80c733e1","tid":342679,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/061345_100e98944a9004fe5a8bdd9408ba3859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F061345_100e98944a9004fe5a8bdd9408ba3859.jpg&h=fc497184&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/061354_6941c7ef662e945a68e18c2ddaa6dbb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F061354_6941c7ef662e945a68e18c2ddaa6dbb5.jpg&h=688d8421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c36070ea86ecc8115db9febe5679c5902b19709","tid":342679,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}